*Pazite* da ne pogrešite put! (Be careful not to make a wrong turn!)
*Ne zaboravite da *pazite* na vreme! (Don't forget to keep an eye on the time!)
*Učenici se *pazili* da ne pogreše odgovor. (The students were careful not to make a mistake with the answer.)
*Uvek *pazite* na svoju bezbednost. (Always take care of your safety.)